videos.description: Arizona's Rawle Alkins gets a steal but misses the layup at the other end. Lauri Markkanen gets the offensive rebound and finishes the play with a dunk.
videos.headline: Lauri Markkanen gets an early dunk against Arizona State

videos.description: Arizona State's Shannon Evans II feeds Obinna Oleka an alley-oop pass from well outside the 3-Point line.
videos.headline: Arizona St. finishes on the long alley-oop try

videos.description: Arizona's Parker Jackson-Cartwright gets the assist as Rawle Alkins throws down a 2-handed alley-oop slam after soaring to the basket.
videos.headline: Rawle Alkins flies through the air for an alley-oop dunk

videos.description: Arizona's Lauri Markkanen is feeling it from long range in the first half against Arizona State, knocking down 3-pointers in three consecutive possessions for the Wildcats.
videos.headline: Arizona's Markkanen hits from deep on three straight possessions

videos.description: With Arizona running in transition, Rawle Alkins elevates to catch the alley-oop lob and finishes for a one-handed dunk.
videos.headline: Arizona's Alkins soars for one-handed alley-oop jam

videos.description: Arizona State head coach Bobby Hurley gets called for a technical foul after going out onto the court during play.
videos.headline: Arizona State head coach called for technical foul

videos.description: In the second half, Arizona's Rawle Alkins sets up Kobi Simmons beautifully for a highlight-reel alley-oop against Arizona State.
videos.headline: Alkins and Simmons connect on alley-oop in Arizona win

videos.description: Arizona's Rawle Alkins gets a block on Arizona State's Tra Holder.
videos.headline: Rawle Alkins protects the rim for Arizona

videos.description: Postgame Breakdown of Arizona's 91-75 victory over Arizona State.
videos.headline: Breaking down Lauri Markkanen's career high 30-point night

videos.description: Lauri Markkanen leads No. 16 Arizona with 30 points while the Wildcats impress the home fans with some highlight-reel dunks in a 91-75 win against Arizona State.
videos.headline: Arizona puts on dunk show in win over Arizona State
